his article is co-written by <span class="mention-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Sidhant Bhutani&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:175192609,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;user&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:null,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/73cb942c-c30e-429b-9317-7f05fa30fe6a_96x96.png&quot;,&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;2eaf8f7c-d0bc-4f84-8c22-c452165fca90&quot;}" data-component-name="MentionToDOM"></span> </p><div><hr></div><p>Leave a comment below to let us know what you think&#8230;</p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://newsletter.theindianotes.com/p/design-of-ondc-vs-marketplaces/comments&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Leave a comment&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://newsletter.theindianotes.com/p/design-of-ondc-vs-marketplaces/comments"><span>Leave a comment</span></a></p><div><hr></div><h3>Do you share our views on ONDC? Share this article with your friends and colleagues to know what they think&#10084;&#65039;</h3><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://newsletter.theindianotes.com/p/design-of-ondc-vs-marketplaces?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://newsletter.theindianotes.com/p/design-of-ondc-vs-marketplaces?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>Share</span></a></p><div><hr></div><p> If you&#8217;re new to The India Notes, here are some of our articles you&#8217;ll love:</p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;a2e322b7-b617-4f55-a71b-bb476a1ee6d9&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Hey there&#128075;, It's Dharmesh Ba! Thanks for your love towards The India Notes newsletter. I run 1990 Research Labs